Name: Delhi Capitals
Posts:
['Dear DC Fans, 

It’s been a rollercoaster of a 3-and-a-half months for all of us here, as we’ve strived to tell you the Delhi Capitals story, through the WPL & IPL, to the best of our ability. 

Our digital team, that has worked tirelessly through the season to bring to you all the content that you’ve always shown so much of love for, needs a bit of a time-out. We’re pressing the ‘pause’ button between May 30 (starting 11 am) to June 4, to recharge, refresh & reboot ourselves. 

Until then, a big Thank You from the bottom of our hearts for your unwavering support and love for Delhi Capitals. We’ll be back soon. Take care.
